{"tid":19557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普與蔡英文通話 美國白宮重申「一個中國」原則","createTime":"2016-12-03T00:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T00:52:28.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9a02faaf4df9853af12838ff64aa2c248b452c","tid":19557,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"川普與小英通話　白宮重申「一個中國」<br />\n<br />\n2016/12/03 07:59&nbsp;3103<br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人川普在昨日與總統蔡英文通電話，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國白宮得知消息後，重申「一個中國」原則，承認北京政府是一中的唯一政權。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n《法新社》報導指出，川普與小英通話一事，可視為打破美國長年來的慣例。但美國國家安全發言人荷恩(Emily Horne)說：「我們對海峽兩岸的政策，長期以來並沒有改變。我們基於《美中三個聯合公報與台灣關係法》，堅定承認『一中』政策，維持海峽兩岸的和平與穩定，是我方根本利益。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161203/1003463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161203%2F1003463&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=af7a5268\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161203/1003463</a>"},{"pid":"54e5842eabb18d81631ca64b87e2942e43a0f1b7","tid":19557,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:48:30.000Z","msg":"快過中國外交部"},{"pid":"810364ba339dfabc8a983c913af883c932269b88","tid":19557,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"一中一台"},{"pid":"25f4f031194f72fa74b9764a71a17116c39f88f5","tid":19557,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:52:28.000Z","msg":"台灣無承認自已係中國唯一政府"}]}